Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:19.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been tall ever since I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:22.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,When we line up for morning assembly, I'm always at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:25.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But I happen to be named "Koizumi".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.91,0:01:26.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.20,0:01:28.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not "Oizumi".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:30.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:33.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.02,0:01:36.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer vacation starts tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.12,0:01:40.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone needs to watch their health.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:46.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially the third years, who will need to prepare for exams soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.03,0:01:50.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful not to catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.02,0:01:54.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The first years should be careful too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.15,0:01:56.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,DAMN IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.10,0:01:58.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,My summon monsters have been annihilated!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:11.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:16.69,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1111,0)\fs26\pos(417,402)}Freshman year summer! I'll definitely find a boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.56,0:02:16.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So you stayed up all night playing games, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.96,0:02:17.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:19.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not very lady like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:22.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And sleeping while standing? Are you a giraffe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.44,0:02:23.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I might have been one in a past life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:24.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite the joker. aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:28.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right then, since you think you're so funny, as punishment you'll continue come to school over the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:30.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!!! Summer vacation starts tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:30.54,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get a vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:33.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to take summer classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.02,0:02:35.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huuuuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:37.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that {\i1}"huh"{\i0}. That's it. Now get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:41.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Being tall has absolutely no advantages.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:43.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I do. I always draw attention to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:50.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:51.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:52.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:54.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you've been trying really hard on the basketball team.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:55.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're great Kotani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:57.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,My name.... is Otani, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:02:59.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Move, you are an amazon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:00.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:01.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:03.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I was being kind and helping you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:04.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you turn around and call me an amazon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:06.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I could call you Kyoshinhei instead…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:07.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, midget!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:08.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:09.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:10.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, All Hanshin-Kyojin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:12.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.57,0:03:14.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please stop calling me that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:18.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,All Hanshin-Kyojin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:21.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The first time Nakano-Sensei called us that way, was on the first day of school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:24.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Does no one want to be class representative?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:27.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what about All Hanshin-Kyojin over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:30.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have Koizumi and Otani do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:33.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:34.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:35.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:37.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! I'm trying to get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:38.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Move, you amazon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:39.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who should move, midget.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:41.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay. The lovers spat ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.96,0:03:42.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not lovers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:49.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,These summer classes are such a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:52.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan, you failed the midterm test so it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:56.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my darling is going to school for basketball practice anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:57.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:03:59.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao-kun, huh? That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:02.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, if I only had a boyfriend too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:06.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No, at the very least, just someone I like. Then I would be more motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:09.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But you sure are weird, Chiharu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:11.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually signed up for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:14.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from the top student of our grade. You sure think differently from the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:19.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I didn't want to be left out by my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:21.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay. We get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:25.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I heard that during summer classes all the different classes are grouped together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:27.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there'll be any nice guys there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:31.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I won't have to see that midget Otani, it'll be heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:33.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really like guys that I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:37.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:39.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to ask the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:42.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:44.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I forget that Otani is a dimwit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:45.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:48.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only here because I snored during the graduation ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:49.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nothing to be proud of!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:51.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,At least I didn't fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:52.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Snoring is so uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:56.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,All Hanshin-Kyojin, will you perform your comedy routine over the summer too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:58.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you to stop calling me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:01.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan, switch seat with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:02.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chaaaaan~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:03.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:04.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.31,0:05:07.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... sitting next to a guy..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:08.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. You can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:09.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:10.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:15.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This... This is the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the worst summer ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:21.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there'll be any nice guys there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:25.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:26.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:29.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't taken attendance yet. You're just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:30.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting with Class 1...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:31.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Abe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:31.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:32.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ida!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:33.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.15,0:05:33.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ueno!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:34.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:35.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Endo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:35.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:36.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Omaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:36.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:44.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can I sit behind you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:46.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, y-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:47.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take a seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:50.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you sit behind Koizumi, you won't be able to see the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:52.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:54.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I'm a little tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:58.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.77,0:06:06.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's love!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:11.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this'll be the best summer ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:25.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dreamy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:27.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:27.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:29.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, nee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:31.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I got something to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:33.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you walk home with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:35.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a delinquent, midget?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:35.98,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:39.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I hang out with you after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:41.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I have something important to say that I can't say here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:44.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How weird... what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:45.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:47.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,like guys like Suzuki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:53.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are easy to read!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:57.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's written all over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.69,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30\c&HC291F9&\3c&H685398&\frz351\pos(373,12)}Suzuki{\frz356}-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.69,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30\c&HC291F9&\3c&H685398&\frz347\pos(301,137)}Love at first sight
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:06:59.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to blackmail me for cash?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:00.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:03.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a super good guy, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:07.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It just happens that I intend to become friends with Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:09.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I might be able to set you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:10.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:11.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:13.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:13.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:14.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:18.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a decent guy after all, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:19.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You only just realized now, idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:24.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And here I thought you were someone who bore a grudge against giraffes in his past life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this thing about giraffes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:27.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, putting that aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:30.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! It's on me, so order whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:33.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A jumbo burger, a fish burger, or a super value set meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:33.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A super value set meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:34.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:35.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:36.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:37.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:39.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...Tanaka-san
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:40.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.78,0:07:41.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka Chiharu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:42.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:44.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Eeeeeeeeh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.10,0:07:48.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So Chiharu-chan is your type, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:50.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot? She's super cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:53.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,From a girl's point of view, I suppose she is kind of cute but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:57.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess short people like other short people, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:07:58.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:00.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I have to tell you something unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:01.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiharu-chan dislikes guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:04.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:06.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:08.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:10.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if she doesn't like guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.58,0:08:12.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cure her of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, we're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:15.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I'll give it my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:17.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we're on the same term.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:21.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, we don't allow shadow boxing in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:24.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:26.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yea… Nakao-chi and I are going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:28.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:30.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:33.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... a friend of mine will be coming too. That's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:35.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:38.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:47.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:48.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:49.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A pool can make you that happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:51.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredibly happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:52.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been to the pool for a whole year!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:54.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither! Me neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.41,0:08:55.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Splash!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:08:58.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:01.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:05.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really different from the school pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:09.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:10.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be fooling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:11.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:15.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! I was so happy, I lost sight of my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:17.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki-kun~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:19.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's go for a swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:20.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:23.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be you didn't really want to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:25.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't, I wouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:25.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:27.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys seem interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:28.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:31.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki-kun, are you attending summer classes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:32.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you failed the midterm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:36.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I had a cold the day of the test, so I couldn't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:38.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:45.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:47.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A topic... I need to find a topic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:50.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But... But I have no idea what to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:52.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Heeey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:53.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:54.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:57.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play beach volleyball, the four of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.23,0:10:00.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:04.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You call standing around in the water and not doing anything fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:07.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know what to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:09.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just because you're trying to pretend to be nice a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:10.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:11.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:14.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do what you normally do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:16.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Just be yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:20.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:21.43,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:22.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:34.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.89,0:10:35.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:38.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, where did Nakao-kun and Nobu-chan go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:40.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:42.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of them went over there a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:44.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,To the water slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:48.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Slide?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:57.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:11:00.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki-kun let's go on that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:11:00.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka-san, lets go on that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:01.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared of things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:03.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:04.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:14.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay if we go play for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:15.98,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:16.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:17.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Water slide!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:18.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,MY FAVORITE!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:19.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:19.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the entrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:20.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it down! And don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.43,0:11:34.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:35.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:37.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It was super fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.10,0:11:41.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! We did it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:43.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, where's Suzuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:45.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. He's been gone for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:47.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:51.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He went somewhere when I met up with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:54.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She left me all alone and ran off to play with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:55.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lost interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:11:59.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:01.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:02.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:04.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a bit thirsty, so I went to get some juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:06.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought enough for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:08.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are thoughtful, Suzuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:09.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:10.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:12.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a warm drink for you, Tanaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:13.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:16.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you seemed cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:18.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:20.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:23.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Should I have gotten you a warm drink too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:24.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:27.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You went on that a lot of times, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:27.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:29.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It was super fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:29.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:31.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not scary at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:32.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:34.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:38.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I can talk with him normally now. This is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:40.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure got tanned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:42.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, right? I tan really quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:47.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiharu-chan doesn't seem to dislike guys anymore either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:49.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy really is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:52.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:53.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya later!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:57.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:12:58.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:01.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiharu-chan and Suzuki-kun's houses are in the same direction...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:03.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:05.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki is a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:07.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And Chiharu doesn't dislike guys anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:09.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She and I were pretty lovey-dovey too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:12.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you guys seemed to be getting along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:14.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You had a pretty good mood going on too, Koizuni.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:18.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:20.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all thanks to you, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:23.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Let's work hard again tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:25.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let's reach for happiness together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:28.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:31.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,....I was still filled with an indescribable feeling of dread.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:37.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki-kun sure is a nice guy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:41.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you've fallen for him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:42.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, no. That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:43.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:45.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:46.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.19,0:13:49.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He walked me home yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:51.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He walked you home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:55.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought that guys were brutish and scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:58.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But Suzuki-kun is very kind. He's not scary at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:00.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:03.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought you were getting along well with Otani yesterday, Chiharu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:05.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well said, Nobu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:06.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what about Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:08.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Otani-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:09.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really easy to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:10.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:13.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably because he's short, so he doesn't seem like a guy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:15.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:24.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani...you're sunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:29.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Man that was harsh. If Otani had heard that, what would he...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:33.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:34.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Otani…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:35.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.71,0:14:36.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Otani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:39.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning to you, Tanaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:42.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday sure was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:42.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So stiff...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:45.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are funny, Otani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.22,0:14:46.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:48.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I am small, therefore I am Kotani.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:52.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:52.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kotani.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:56.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell the teacher that Kotani will be absent today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:14:58.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:14:59.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotani...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:00.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:06.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:09.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to call me Kotani, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:15.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:16.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:17.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to comfort me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:18.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:21.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I was just worried about you. What's with that sarcastic attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:23.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's being sarcastic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:25.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if you got called small?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:26.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a man, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:29.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm small so I don't count as a guy-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:33.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:37.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Big or small, as long as you have a **** you're a man, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:38.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls shouldn't say that word...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:39.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:41.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you always been called small?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Acting like this just because a girl said it is pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:49.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get so depressed over stuff like this, no one will ever like you, dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:52.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.. Pisses me off...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:57.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha.. That idiot's punch really woke me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:02.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:03.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:04.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:06.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:08.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Class has already started...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:10.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:12.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good at getting up early in summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:13.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:17.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't get up early in the winter either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:18.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:20.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:21.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:23.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah. Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:25.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Um..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:26.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:27.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:29.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:32.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, Tanaka-san seemed scared of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.96,0:16:36.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki-kun sure is a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:42.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh.... she's just not comfortable around guys. It's not your fault, Suzuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:45.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really good at talking to girls either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:46.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:47.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:48.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:51.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,for some reason, I find you easy to talk with, Koizumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:52.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:58.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably because we're almost the same height,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:01.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't think of you as a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:03.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uuuh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:05.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:11.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:11.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:16.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So Tanka-san doesn't hate me then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:17.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:18.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:21.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huuuuh?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:23.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me... you like Chiharu-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:25.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:26.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:28.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm just hot. Very hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:29.98,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:32.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:36.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:38.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He definitely likes her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:40.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That look totally gave it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:42.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Oizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:45.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You were at me just a minute ago. What are you so depressed for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:49.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, just forget about what I said before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:51.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:54.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I normally pretend to not care,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.31,0:17:56.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,but it really hurts when it's coming from the person I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:59.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:00.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's payback for before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:02.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:03.74,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not giving up on Chiharu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:05.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to keep trying from tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.49,0:18:07.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:09.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get so depressed over stuff like this, no one will ever like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:11.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were my grandpa's last words.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:12.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:15.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're here, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:18.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd been alone, who knows where I'd have to run off too and hide?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:21.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:24.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to keep trying too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:27.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:28.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:30.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The summer festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:32.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I invited Suzuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:34.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani invited Chiharu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:41.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So much for my sexy yukata seduction plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:43.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It just doesn't look right on a tall women like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.03,0:18:45.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:48.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiharu-chan and the others aren't here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:51.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The train was packed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:53.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that maybe they got lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:56.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.35,0:18:57.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't recognize you for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:18:58.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:18:59.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't suit me at all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:00.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:01.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But you really went all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:03.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:05.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I was late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:05.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's here, she's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:07.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.57,0:19:09.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki-kun is with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:11.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I bumped into him on my way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:21.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:24.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,To prevent her from getting bumped. he switched positions with her, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:27.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's clear...It's clear, but it's clearly upsetting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:32.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,They look pretty good together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:35.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,They're like a couple that have just started going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.45,0:19:40.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:41.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:44.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:46.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:53.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I give up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:54.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels like the ending of the comedy show.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:20:00.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:03.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:06.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Risa-chan? Otani-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:08.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Waah! It broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:08.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me give it a go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:11.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:20.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Otani next we'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:22.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh? Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.17,0:20:23.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:24.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:25.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:28.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so short. I thought you got lost in the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:29.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:30.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:33.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you say that? That was pretty awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.78,0:20:34.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:35.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get some grilled cuttlefish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:41.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani might be small...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:43.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,but his hand still feels like a guy's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:51.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We may always be fighting, but our personalities kind of suit each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:54.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And we both have height complexes too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:21:00.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you. Please go out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:01.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:07.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Not long after that, Chiharu-chan and Suzuki-kun became a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:10.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! I feel better now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:11.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:15.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Chiharu-chan looked pretty good together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:18.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But you and Suzuki-kun didn't work out at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:19.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.45,0:21:20.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.81,0:21:23.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I can find a girlfriend quickly enough if I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:25.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh is that so? I'd like to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.90,0:21:30.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I challenge you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:33.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see who can get someone faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.57,0:21:36.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I get if I win?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:37.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy you whatever game you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:40.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I win, you'll buy me a new pair of basketball shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.64,0:21:43.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.44,0:21:45.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.81,0:23:28.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! An ex-girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.47,0:23:30.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Otani's?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.04,0:23:30.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.60,0:23:33.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,LOVELY COMPLEX - LOVE.COM
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.04,0:23:36.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Next: The Ex-Girlfriend Love Triangle?!
